data.description: This 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom gem nestled in Conway, Arkansas, offers an incredible canvas for your creativity and vision. This home comes with 3300 sqft, large eat in kitchen, large backyard, Dining room, wood burning fireplace, 4 bedrooms downstairs, bonus room and 5th bedroom upstairs with a full bath. Schedule your showing today.
